creator: AliHelper
descriptionHtml:
★ What AliHelper is for:
- Check the rating of sellers in AliExpress store (detailed information about the seller's seniority, quality of service, buy only from verified sellers)
- History of changes in the price of products (price tracking for the last 3 months)
- We will notify about the reduction of the price for a profitable purchase

★ We know everything about Chinese stores and price tracking - trust us and you will know about all the discounts and buy with maximum savings!

★ How to use the app:
- Open popular official AliExpress app/online store
- Go to the sellers page
- Click "Share" and choose the AliHelper icon
- It's done! Here is detailed information about the seller/product
- Add items to "Favorites" and we'll notify you when the price drops
descriptionShort: Price tracker tool for most popular China store, Aliexpress price comparison

As soon as possible we respond to all sorts and make the application better for you.

title: AliHelper - Ali price tracker

creator: AliHelper
descriptionHtml:
🛍 With AliAssistant, you'll only make good-value and safe purchases of products from China in the official AliExpress ™ store. If you are an active user of the Ali app, you will relish the opportunity to buy Chinese goods even cheaper and receive orders even faster. All this will become a reality if you install AliHelper.


✅ What is the AliHelper application for?


★ Find out a seller's rating
Here you'll find an objective rating for a seller on AliExpress free shopping app (from 0 to 100%), which is compiled after analysis of all available indicators: the quality of the products, the standard of the store's service, delivery speed, number of reviews, and more.


★ Follow discounts on Aliexpress
You can see the actual discounts, even before coupons and cashback are applied. This feature will be really useful during sales and will allow you to make only good-value purchases in the Ali app.


★ Find similar products from China cheaper
A feature for viewing up to 50 alternative options for the desired product from different sellers, which can be sorted by any criteria you need.


★ Push notifications
You'll be able to receive messages informing you about discounts on Ali with price tracker. Just save the product you need, and AliHelper will send you a notification when its price decreases.


★ See actual photos of the product
In the AliHelper application, you can view and compare photos from the seller on the China shopping app store with actual photos of the products taken by users.


★ Read real users reviews
This function allows you to see reviews of product from with Ali online store. It will allow you to study both negative and positive reviews about Chinese products.

We know everything about AliExpress app; trust us, and you'll be able to find out the whole truth about a seller’s reliability, follow actual discounts, and choose the best goods from China. Smarter shopping, better living!


⏳Coming soon


★ Package tracking
With this function you can easily track the package from the Ali online store using a tracking code.


★ Aliexpress Discount Coupons
With discount coupons your shopping on will become even more profitable and comfortable!
descriptionShort: Aliexpress shopping canada assistant app, goods from china with price history!

If you are an active user of the Ali app, you will relish the opportunity to buy Chinese goods even cheaper and receive orders even faster. All this will become a reality if you install AliHelper.


✅ What is the AliHelper application for?


★ Find out a seller's rating
Here you'll find an objective rating for a seller on AliExpress free shopping app (from 0 to 100%), which is compiled after analysis of all available indicators: the quality of the products, the standard of the store's service, delivery speed, number of reviews, and more.


★ Follow discounts on Aliexpress
You can see the actual discounts, even before coupons and cashback are applied. This feature will be really useful during sales and will allow you to make only good-value purchases in the Ali app.


★ Find similar products from China cheaper
A feature for viewing up to 50 alternative options for the desired product from different sellers, which can be sorted by any criteria you need.


★ Push notifications
You'll be able to receive messages informing you about discounts on Ali with price tracker. Just save the product you need, and AliHelper will send you a notification when its price decreases.


★ See actual photos of the product
In the AliHelper application, you can view and compare photos from the seller on the China shopping app store with actual photos of the products taken by users.


★ Read real users reviews
This function allows you to see reviews of product from with Ali online store. It will allow you to study both negative and positive reviews about Chinese products.

We know everything about AliExpress app; trust us, and you'll be able to find out the whole truth about a seller’s reliability, follow actual discounts, and choose the best goods from China. Smarter shopping, better living!


⏳Coming soon


★ Package tracking
With this function you can easily track the package from the Ali online store using a tracking code.


★ Aliexpress Discount Coupons
With discount coupons your shopping on will become even more profitable and comfortable!

title: AliHelper - Price History tool

creator: AliHelper
descriptionHtml:
🛍 With AliAssistant, you'll only make good-value and safe purchases of products from China in the official AliExpress ™ store. If you are an active user of the Ali app, you will relish the opportunity to buy Chinese goods even cheaper and receive orders even faster. All this will become a reality if you install AliHelper.


✅ What is the AliHelper application for?


★ Find out a seller's rating
Here you'll find an objective rating for a seller on AliExpress free shopping app (from 0 to 100%), which is compiled after analysis of all available indicators: the quality of the products, the standard of the store's service, delivery speed, number of reviews, and more.


★ Follow discounts on Aliexpress
You can see the actual discounts, even before coupons and cashback are applied. This feature will be really useful during sales and will allow you to make only good-value purchases in the Ali app.


★ Find similar products from China cheaper
A feature for viewing up to 50 alternative options for the desired product from different sellers, which can be sorted by any criteria you need.


★ Push notifications
You'll be able to receive messages informing you about discounts on Ali with price tracker. Just save the product you need, and AliHelper will send you a notification when its price decreases.


★ See actual photos of the product
In the AliHelper application, you can view and compare photos from the seller on the China shopping app store with actual photos of the products taken by users.


★ Read real users reviews
This function allows you to see reviews of product from with Ali online store. It will allow you to study both negative and positive reviews about Chinese products.

We know everything about AliExpress app; trust us, and you'll be able to find out the whole truth about a seller’s reliability, follow actual discounts, and choose the best goods from China. Smarter shopping, better living!


⏳Coming soon


★ Package tracking
With this function you can easily track the package from the Ali online store using a tracking code.


★ Aliexpress Discount Coupons
With discount coupons your shopping on will become even more profitable and comfortable!

🛍 With AliAssistant, you'll only make good-value and safe purchases of products from China in the official AliExpress ™ store. If you are an active user of the Ali app, you will relish the opportunity to buy Chinese goods even cheaper and receive orders even faster. All this will become a reality if you install AliHelper.


✅ What is the AliHelper application for?


★ Find out a seller's rating
Here you'll find an objective rating for a seller on AliExpress free shopping app (from 0 to 100%), which is compiled after analysis of all available indicators: the quality of the products, the standard of the store's service, delivery speed, number of reviews, and more.


★ Follow discounts on Aliexpress
You can see the actual discounts, even before coupons and cashback are applied. This feature will be really useful during sales and will allow you to make only good-value purchases in the Ali app.


★ Find similar products from China cheaper
A feature for viewing up to 50 alternative options for the desired product from different sellers, which can be sorted by any criteria you need.


★ Push notifications
You'll be able to receive messages informing you about discounts on Ali with price tracker. Just save the product you need, and AliHelper will send you a notification when its price decreases.


★ See actual photos of the product
In the AliHelper application, you can view and compare photos from the seller on the China shopping app store with actual photos of the products taken by users.


★ Read real users reviews
This function allows you to see reviews of product from with Ali online store. It will allow you to study both negative and positive reviews about Chinese products.

We know everything about AliExpress app; trust us, and you'll be able to find out the whole truth about a seller’s reliability, follow actual discounts, and choose the best goods from China. Smarter shopping, better living!


⏳Coming soon


★ Package tracking
With this function you can easily track the package from the Ali online store using a tracking code.


★ Aliexpress Discount Coupons
With discount coupons your shopping on will become even more profitable and comfortable!
descriptionShort: Price tracker tool for most popular China store, Aliexpress price comparison

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Making AiHelper even better:
- NEW! Price change chart with setting range: from 1 to 6 months
- Added feature of viewing customer reviews
- Added the possibility of viewing the number of reviews in similar commodities
- Errors fixed in which the application could work incorrectly
Please, write on the bugs found/wishes at pricetracking.helper@gmail.com
As soon as possible we respond to all sorts and make the application better for you.
Sincerely, AiHelper team!
